OL,3,C'A trial of cowardice': Gisele
OL,4,CPelicot's final statement in mass rape
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,FGisele Pelicot, the victim in a mass
OL,8,Frape trial in France, has accused the
OL,9,Fdozens of men alleged to have raped
OL,10,Fher of "cowardice" as she delivers her
OL,11,Ffinal statement at the French court.
OL,13,FPelicot told the courtroom in Avignon
OL,14,Fwith many of the accused in the
OL,15,Fcourtroom: "For me this is the trial
OL,16,Fof cowardice, there is no other way to
OL,17,Fdescribe it."
