OL,3,C'A trial of cowardice': Gisele
OL,4,CPelicot's final statement in mass rape
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,FHer ex-husband, Dominique Pelicot, is
OL,8,Faccused of drugging and raping her,
OL,9,Fand inviting some 50 other men to do
OL,10,Fthe same over a nine-year period.
OL,12,FDelivering her final statement before
OL,13,Fprosecutors and defence teams make
OL,14,Ftheir final arguments, she said
OL,15,Fsociety needed to change the way it
OL,16,Fsees rape.
OL,18,F"It's time that the macho, patriarchal
OL,19,Fsociety that trivialises rape
OL,20,Fchanges," she said.
