OL,7,F"You will die lying"
OL,9,FOn Tuesday, the court heard from the
OL,10,FDominique Pelicot who has already
OL,11,Fadmitted to the charges levelled
OL,12,Fagainst him.
OL,14,FHe told the court in September: "I am
OL,15,Fa rapist, like the other men in this
OL,16,Froom".
