OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,FDominique denies doing anything to his
OL,8,Fchildren or grandchildren and went on
OL,9,Fto describe the sexual abuse he
OL,10,Fsuffered during his childhood, but
OL,11,Ftold the court that this does not an
OL,12,Fexcuse for anything he has done.
OL,14,F"There'll forever be 51 people who
OL,15,Fhave defiled me."
OL,17,FA total of 50 men were identified by
OL,18,Fpolice from films labelled and stored
OL,19,Fby Dominique Pelicot. The men on trial
OL,20,Fface up to 20 years in prison.
