OL,7,F"Rape is rape"
OL,9,FOver the course of the trial, Gisele
OL,10,FPelicot has become a symbol of the
OL,11,Ffight against sexual violence in
OL,12,FFrance, acknowledged for waiving her
OL,13,Fanonymity in the case.
OL,15,F"Rape is rape", she said in an address
OL,16,Fto the accused. "When you walk into a
OL,17,Fbedroom and see a motionless body, at
OL,18,Fwhat point (do you decide) not to
OL,19,Freact."
