OL,7,F"Why did you not leave immediately to
OL,8,Freport it to the police?"
OL,10,FShe said she would never forgive her
OL,11,Fhusband.
OL,13,FPreviously she said she does not want
OL,14,Fto feel shame for the alleged crimes
OL,15,Fcommitted against her. She repeated
OL,16,Fthis thought today when asked about
OL,17,Fcontinuing to use her alleged abuser's
OL,18,Fand ex-husband's surname.
