OL,7,FShe spoke of her grandchildren: "They
OL,8,Fshouldn't be ashamed of carrying that
OL,9,Fname".
OL,11,F"I could have died"
OL,13,FGisele Pelicot also spoke about the
OL,14,Fhealth implications of the drugging
OL,15,Fand rape. She told the court that: "I
OL,16,Flost ten years of my life" to the
OL,17,Fmedical consequences. "This scar will
OL,18,Fnever heal".
