OL,7,FShe adds that her health concerns felt
OL,8,F"like a death sentence" and that in
OL,9,Fthe depths of her medical issues she
OL,10,F"thought (she'd) either die or end up
OL,11,Fin a mental hospital".
OL,13,FGisele Pelicot went on to question why
OL,14,Fthis happened. "As I didn't want to go
OL,15,Fto a swingers' club, he thought he'd
OL,16,Ffound the solution by putting me to
OL,17,Fsleep," she said.
OL,19,FA verdict from a panel of five judges
OL,20,Fis it expected to be handed down on
OL,21,FDecember 20.
